column14: Caleigh is a very loving and hardworking girl. She participates in as many clubs/sports as she can at school, a few being cheer, volleyball, track, and FCA (fellowship of christian athletes). Caleigh dedicates most of her time to achieving her academic goals and volunteering at the local food pantry. She would love to become a part of the Lincoln G.O.L.D because she enjoys meeting new people and bettering herself alongside others.
